# 🎙 Bengo Workflow — Your Guide to Getting Stuff Done

Welcome to the Bengo Workflow app! It's where episodes get made, tasks get ticked off, and nothing falls through the cracks. Think of it as the behind-the-scenes magic that keeps the Bengoverse running smoothly.

Bookmark the link. Open it every day. That's it, really — but read on for the full picture.

---

## The big idea

Every podcast we make follows a workflow — from booking the studio right through to the invoice being paid. This app tracks all of it, episode by episode, so everyone knows what they're doing, what's next, and what's overdue.

No more "I thought you were doing that." No more sticky notes. No more Monday (RIP).

---

## Finding your way around

The sidebar on the left is your nav. Here's what each section does:

| Section | What it's for |
|---|---|
| ⬡ **Dashboard** | The big picture — overdue tasks, open work, headline stats |
| 🎙 **Podcasts** | All the shows we're making, one card per podcast |
| ✅ **All Tasks** | Every task across every episode — filterable by status, podcast or role |
| 👤 **My Tasks** | Your personal view — episode tasks AND to-dos in one place |
| 📊 **Gantt** | The timeline view — episodes and tasks plotted across the calendar |
| 📝 **To-Do** | Freestanding tasks that aren't tied to a specific episode |
| 👥 **People** | The team |

